The little new ones are looking for weapons in different ways.
Former soldier Victor Baranets tried to buy illegal weapons in the mid-1990s when he was preparing to publish an article on the subject.
The diagrams, according to him, have not changed.
We gave him a photo album in which there was "everything we want."
